4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring professionals without prior experience. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes weekly, with a maximum of 16 students per class. Participants will gain foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration while mastering cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The bootcamp emphasizes risk management, data loss prevention strategies, and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions. The course is available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop